<section id="contact" class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center max-w-2xl">
		<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Contáctanos</h2>
		<p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10">
			¿Interesado en saber más o solicitar una demostración personalizada? Rellena el formulario y nos pondremos en contacto contigo.
		</p>
		<form class="bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-xl space-y-6">
			<div>
				<label for="name" class="block text-left text-gray-300 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Nombre Completo</label>
				<input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="w-full p-3 rounded-md bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8bb303]" placeholder="Tu nombre" required>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="email" class="block text-left text-gray-300 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Correo Electrónico</label>
				<input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="w-full p-3 rounded-md bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8bb303]" placeholder="tu.correo@ejemplo.com" required>
			</div>
			<div>
				<label for="message" class="block text-left text-gray-300 text-sm font-medium mb-2">Tu Mensaje</label>
				<textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" class="w-full p-3 rounded-md bg-gray-700 border border-gray-600 text-white focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-[#8bb303]" placeholder="Me gustaría saber más sobre..." required></textarea>
			</div>
			<button type="submit" class="w-full bg-[#8bb303] hover:bg-[#7aa202] text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg">
				Enviar Mensaje
			</button>
		</form>
	</div>
</section>